WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.620 --> 00:00:02.620
What?

2
00:00:02.620 --> 00:00:03.620
I need to tell her.

3
00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:04.620
No, you don't.

4
00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:07.450
What happened to you?

5
00:00:07.450 --> 00:00:10.449
You love this James dude so much that you've been willing to do anything?

6
00:00:10.449 --> 00:00:13.740
I don't even recognize you anymore.

7
00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:15.019
Yes.

8
00:00:15.019 --> 00:00:18.120
I want to be with Nia.

9
00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:20.120
But I would never, ever stoop this low.

10
00:00:20.120 --> 00:00:36.820
Now let go of me.

11
00:00:36.820 --> 00:00:43.850
Why are you rejecting me?

12
00:00:43.850 --> 00:00:45.850
Please don't tell me it's because of silly.

13
00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:49.880
Look, I don't know how to make it more abundantly clear that I don't want her.

14
00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:58.200
Look, when you were in the hospital, I didn't have a chance to explain things and I didn't want to sound like I was coming in between you girls.

15
00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:02.200
But Nia, you have to believe me that all I want.

